snippet.title: PlayStation - Tour Party - Sotsugyou Ryokou ni Ikou (1998) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Tour Party: Sotsugyou Ryokou ni Ikou is a Miscellaneous game, developed by Japan Media Programming and published by Takara, which was released in Japan in 1998.
